Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:18.60,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:24.31,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.05,0:00:30.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:36.73,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:41.83,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:48.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:52.61,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:57.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:01:00.95,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:06.29,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:12.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,that blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:17.30,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:23.84,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:38.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lt. Hikaru Ichijo, Vermilion Team,\NValkyrie Fighter Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:41.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wounded at Torishimaoki while\Ndefending the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:45.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lacerations across entire body.\NCurrently in recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:49.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Irregular brainwave activity detected, the\Nresult of contusions to the head area.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:02.95,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(78,132)}PHANTASM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:12.89,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\Nwe thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:19.13,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Lynn Minmay's first concert\Nwill now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:42.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,First up is her debut song,\N"My Boyfriend is a Pilot."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.64,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:55.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Min...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.64,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:56.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:03:01.48,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:02.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,L-O-V-E! Happy Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:05.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shining, making a rapid descent
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:08.48,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then BOOM! he makes a sudden climb
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:14.29,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leaving a long trail of vapor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:21.16,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He traces two big hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:26.40,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A love sign in the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:37.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru, help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay! I'm coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seated and ready to take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,VT-102! Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:31.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not reading your transponder signal.\NWhat's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:33.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know anything\Nabout that, you old lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:42.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady, huh? Don't tell me you...\NYou're a civilian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:01.00,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.83,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,At approximately 2:00 this afternoon,\Ncivilian Hikaru Ichijo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:08.67,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,hijacked a Valkyrie variable fighter,\Nbut due to his inexperience
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:13.13,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,he failed to escape\Nand was shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I blew it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:27.86,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please, Hikaru!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:29.86,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Come save me! Hurry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.16,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. I guess I'd better ask\NSempai for some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:42.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to become a military pilot\Nso you can go rescue Minmay, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:49.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably better than being a civilian who\Nswipes military planes and gets shot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:59.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, Hikaru?\NYou'd better salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:00.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,O...Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hikaru Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:06.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa Hayase. Hikaru Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that name somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:12.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that civilian!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're that old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the guy who got shot down\Na while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:22.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's that civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:25.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:28.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you pass your aptitude tests, she'll be\Nyour operator and your superior officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:29.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Y...Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:32.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This one? Pass the aptitude tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:37.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you hijacked that plane\Nto rescue your girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:41.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but make sure you don't crash\Nand burn on your tests too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:13.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Hikaru! You passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you're now a full-fledged soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to do your best and\Nrescue Minmay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet, Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:40.18,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:45.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:51.59,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:58.31,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:03.40,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:10.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That does it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:28.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've launched in an Armored Valkyrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lt. Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:34.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to behave\Nand not run off on your own again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to try to save Minmay\Nagain, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep running off like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep chasing after that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I love her! So I've got no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:51.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,See if I care if\Nyou get shot down again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna get taken out this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:31.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Armored Valkyrie has been\Nheavily damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Ichijo says he's returning to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:34.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shot down again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:35.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:38.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think he's gonna go out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:40.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he'll go out over and\Nover for that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he'll even go on all fours!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No {\i1}way{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I could see it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get shot down every time\NI'm in a Valkyrie
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I might have a chance on\Nthis special bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait for me, Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:08.37,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:12.31,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Early this morning, 1st Lt. Ichijo Hikaru,\Nalso known as the Crash King,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:16.47,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,tried unsuccessfully to pedal his\Nbicycle into outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.42,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Such behavior is extremely\Ndangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:23.38,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,so we ask that you please don't\Nattempt it at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:29.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, if it's all right with you,\Nwe'd like to help you rescue Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, you should've just asked, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:34.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:48.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you and the others\Noffered to help me, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:51.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, once we get back,\Nyou'll have to do as you're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:58.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A second wave is coming in from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:12.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's sneak aboard the enemy ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:19.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How will we look for Minmay\Nonce we're aboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:23.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, why not disguise yourself\Nas one of the giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A disguise, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:43.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it will take long\Nfor someone to spot us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:45.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll worry about that when it happens.\NHere goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.69,Zent,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Muetema!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about the bumpy ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:48.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! It won't move at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to make\Na break for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:27.72,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.17,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is like a raging wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:34.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:36.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:38.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And she has such a nice voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:40.75,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It never leads to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:39.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:42.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'd better hurry up and rescue her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:48.61,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where you'd expect
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:46.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hayase, please let me do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. That would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:14:01.96,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will go forward loving you the way I do now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:54.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:09.68,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts beating as one
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:12.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay! I'm here to rescue you,\Njust like I promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:13.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That just won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:16.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't do? But why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:22.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Hikaru. Kaifun says I\Ncan't go out with soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:25.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would Kaifun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I hate soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never give Minmay to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:33.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you heard what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:42.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Then I'll give up being a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:44.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.62,0:14:45.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.29,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick, hop on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:56.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:58.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Missiles are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:59.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:05.66,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With him after school, on my way home
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:12.58,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the corner of that same old intersection
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? I'm taking us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:17.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He made sure no one else was around
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:23.84,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then without warning, he kissed me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:30.57,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I was so angry, I led him to think,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, but, but
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My head was dizzy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And my heart was fluttering
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:40.58,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.11,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Four, three, two, one,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.76,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:52.42,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My body floats up and I fly away on the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still dangerous here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:57.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be saved if I transform the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:58.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Transform...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:06.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does it look brighter down there to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:34.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:35.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:41.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we can climb up over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:42.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An airlock for giants, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:10.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are all spaceships?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:12.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a huge fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:19.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A skirmish?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:24.29,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the closer we get, you can\Nsee the scale is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:27.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's big enough to swallow the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:32.41,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was having a bad dream or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:01.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it, Hikaru!\NYou were peeking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:07.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since we were\Nalone together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:14.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure has. About a year, since you were\Npicked Miss Macross and became a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it really been a year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:19.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds long, but it just flew by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen to us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:29.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:38.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you sure\Nthat's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be trouble if somebody\Nsees you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:50.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that light just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:53.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe some paparazzi got\Nsome pictures of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:54.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:58.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If those pictures get out,\Nthe whole town will be talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:28.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally rescued you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:29.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's gonna happen to us now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:53.66,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the midnight bell tolled,\Nthe magic spell wore off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:20:00.81,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Down the staircase she rushed,\Nas if trying to outrun it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:07.71,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And at the top of the stairs,\Na single glass slipper...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a new song?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:16.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's an old one I wrote\Nmyself, called "Cinderella."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:21.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it'll be a hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:23.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sure it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:26.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are getting further\Nand further apart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:30.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll always be friends, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Minmay, what would you want to be\Nif you couldn't become a singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:40.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A bride, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:41.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I bet you'd make a great bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:46.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:50.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all over for us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:52.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:55.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing that says we're\Ngoing to just die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:21:01.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Hikaru. But I wish I could have worn\Na wedding dress just once before I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we have\Na wedding ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:22.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. That would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:38.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Are you sure you're okay\Nwith someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:44.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When we wake up from this dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.02,0:21:50.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get married for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:52.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:54.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:22:00.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy enough to say, but won't\Nyou just change your mind later?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:04.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been fickle like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:07.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:09.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who said we should\Nhave a wedding ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:13.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You never meant it! You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:19.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to have doubts. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:21.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:24.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I live in a different world from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:26.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:29.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I still... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all it is, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:35.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:36.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:40.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.09,0:23:04.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Protoculture!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:07.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Minmay turn into\NCaptain Hayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:10.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,\Nyou're a soldier too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.68,0:23:24.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:30.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure was a bad one...
