Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:43.32,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru Ichijo is still unable\Nto return to duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:48.98,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, a Queadluun-Rau team led\Nby Milia launches its attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.05,0:23:52.22,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,But Milia's target isn't the Macross;
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:54.02,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,it's Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.23,0:23:57.46,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:59.83,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"PINEAPPLE SALAD"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.63,0:24:02.23,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(100,140)}PINEAPPLE SALAD
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.79,0:24:22.62,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:29.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.83,0:24:36.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.23,0:24:43.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.78,0:24:50.15,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.85,0:24:56.41,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.81,0:25:04.08,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.35,0:25:15.59,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
